title.narrative: Not Any Girl - UK Aid Match Project

description.narrative: To empower vulnerable girls and community members in 3 counties of Kenya to speak out and report cases of violence; work with duty bearers to increase state accountability and effectiveness to respond to violence against girls (VAG) and build the capacity of women’s rights networks members to strengthen community-based protection mechanisms against VAG
